    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Property of materials, such as paper or mat board, or processing methods that are expected to allow items to be stored for extended periods of time without loss of quality.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
